### 🔴 HIGH — No Security Headers (OWASP A05: Security Misconfiguration)

The app sends default Express headers, which include the `X-Powered-By: Express` fingerprint and lack all protective headers (CSP, HSTS, X-Content-Type-Options, etc.).

